  "notes": [
    "This study compares GenMine TOP (dual DNA-RNA panel) with FoundationOne CDx (DNA-only panel) for sarcoma genomic profiling",
    "GenMine TOP showed superior performance in detecting fusion genes, particularly important for translocation-related sarcomas",
    "The tumor-normal matched design of GenMine TOP enables identification of germline pathogenic variants",
    "Study used real-world data from Japan's nationwide C-CAT database with 1046 patients"
  ]
